data.description: This beautiful home is Located 5 minutes from Jackson and Historical Sutter Creek. Light and bright living room with large Picture window. The view from the back deck is truly amazing and the sunsets are breathtaking. In the kitchen there are Stainless Steel appliances and Granite Counter tops. The Hardwood floors are so rich and beautiful with many color variations. Newer HVAC, and Tankless water heater. Three bedrooms upstairs and bonus room and bedroom downstairs. The neighborhood is very quiet and peaceful.
